HEADWORD: Ambreic
<hw>Am*bre"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to ambrein; -- said of a certain acid produced by
digesting ambrein in nitric acid.</def>⟦br⟧
